        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>A cloak of swirling colors shrouds the target. Creatures are @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Dazzled]{Dazzled} while adjacent to it, and attacking the target causes a brilliant flash of light. A creature that hits the target with a melee attack must attempt a Will save.The creature is temporarily immune until the end of its turn; this effect has the incapacitation trait.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The attacker is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The attacker is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Blinded]{Blinded} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The attacker is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stunned]{Stunned} for 1 round.</p>"
